\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\Vert uv^{T}XX^{T}\right\Vert _{2}\le\left\Vert uv^{T}\right\Vert _{2}\left\Vert XX^{T}\right\Vert _{2}=1
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
Notice that in our case 
\begin_inset Formula $YX^{T}\in\Psi$
\end_inset

